location.fullValue: Lincoln Plan, The Overlook at Creekside

data.description: Open House on Saturday, 11/4/23 12-2. Come see this great two story home conveniently located minutes from shopping, entertainment, schools, grocery store and much more.  The home features an open floor plan with all tile floors downstairs.  All bedrooms are upstairs as well as a flex room that will make a great office or sitting area.  This is a lovely home for a first time buyer or tenant investment property with plenty of room for a family to enjoy.  The family friendly neighborhood features a community pool and park/playground. The refrigerator, washer, dryer and several boxes of unused floor tiles will convey with the sale.
